%% Dispatch flow sequence
sequenceDiagram
  participant Customer
  participant RealtimeDB
  participant CloudFunction
  participant GoogleMatrix
  participant RidersNode
  participant RiderApp
  participant Admin

  Customer->>RealtimeDB: push new order (pickup coords)
  RealtimeDB->>CloudFunction: onCreate(order)
  CloudFunction->>RidersNode: read available riders
  CloudFunction->>GoogleMatrix: ETA matrix (orig=pickup,dests=riders)
  GoogleMatrix-->>CloudFunction: ETA results
  CloudFunction->>RidersNode: transaction(reserve rider)
  CloudFunction->>RealtimeDB: update order.assignedRiderId,status=Assigned
  CloudFunction->>RiderApp: push notification (new order)
  RiderApp->>RealtimeDB: accept/update location
  RealtimeDB->>CloudFunction: onRiderNodeChange -> compute ETA update
  CloudFunction->>RealtimeDB: update order.etaSeconds
  CloudFunction->>Customer: proximity push when near destination
  Admin->>RealtimeDB: monitor orders & riders
